<i>[The Starry Love]
[Adapted from "The Starry Love" by Yi Du Jun Hua]</i>

20
00:01:45,080 --> 00:01:48,480
<i>[Episode 17]</i>

21
00:01:48,480 --> 00:01:52,440
Tell me. What's the reason behind your rejection?

22
00:01:52,440 --> 00:01:54,400
If you wish to extinguish the Southern Brightness Sacred Fire,

23
00:01:54,400 --> 00:01:56,180
you need to acquire a magic item from the Rain Deity.

24
00:01:56,180 --> 00:01:57,840
It's called the Purifying Vial.

25
00:01:57,840 --> 00:02:01,400
It contains the Dew of the Sun and Moon, and it's connected to the Jade Pool.

26
00:02:01,400 --> 00:02:06,720
Every year, the Rain Deity will pray for the human race.

27
00:02:06,720 --> 00:02:10,920
I heard that it's the only thing that can extinguish the Southern Brightness Sacred Fire.

28
00:02:10,920 --> 00:02:13,060
But we left the Heavenly Realm without permission.

29
00:02:13,060 --> 00:02:15,680
If we return to the Heavenly Realm right now,

30
00:02:15,680 --> 00:02:21,240
not only will we be punished, but we'll also lose our chance to come back and save Youqin.

31
00:02:24,100 --> 00:02:27,280
You should continue eating. Come with me. Come on.

32
00:02:31,820 --> 00:02:35,281
Are you trying to return to the Heavenly Realm again?

33
00:02:35,281 --> 00:02:37,680
The Heavenly Emperor is heartless.

34
00:02:37,680 --> 00:02:39,960
If you go back now, you'll definitely be punished.

35
00:02:39,960 --> 00:02:43,581
The Heavenly Thunder, the heavenly ordeals, your human body cannot withstand any of them.

36
00:02:43,581 --> 00:02:46,340
Besides, didn't the Jade Deity tell us already?

37
00:02:46,340 --> 00:02:48,060
You just need to make the soul shards fall in love with you.

38
00:02:48,060 --> 00:02:51,781
After we retrieve the other two soul shards, we'll call Fiery and merge the soul shards with him.

39
00:02:51,781 --> 00:02:54,950
The Southern Brightness Sacred Fire has nothing to do with you.

40
00:02:54,950 --> 00:02:58,821
Although that's the case, the Southern Brightness Sacred Fire is very important to Fiery.

41
00:02:58,821 --> 00:03:02,020
If I bring him away by force, both he nor I won't be able to rest at ease.

42
00:03:02,020 --> 00:03:05,220
Shouldn't the Devil of Void resort to anything to achieve her goals?

43
00:03:05,220 --> 00:03:08,060
Tan Tan, you've been going against the ways of the devil lately.

44
00:03:08,060 --> 00:03:09,760
What's wrong with being a devil? Can't a devil make friends?

45
00:03:09,760 --> 00:03:12,420
Can't a devil fulfill her friend's wish?

46
00:03:13,460 --> 00:03:15,580
I will not let him suffer again.

47
00:03:15,580 --> 00:03:18,960
I will fulfill his wish. I've made up my mind.

48
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:21,660
Then... What if you die in the Heavenly Realm then?

49
00:03:21,660 --> 00:03:24,460
How can I face Young Master when he comes back?

50
00:03:24,460 --> 00:03:27,700
What else can I do? Do you want me to wait for them to send me the vial?

51
00:03:27,700 --> 00:03:29,093
I...

52
00:03:33,560 --> 00:03:38,400
Isn't it easier if we ask the immortals to send someone down here?

53
00:03:39,080 --> 00:03:41,640
You want the deities to send their magic item to you?

54
00:03:41,640 --> 00:03:45,280
Is she out of her mind? Or am I out of my mind here?

55
00:03:45,280 --> 00:03:47,900
Sister-in-law, since you're saying that, I assume you've come up with something.

56
00:03:47,900 --> 00:03:49,633
Of course.

57
00:03:49,633 --> 00:03:53,260
Ever since the wedding pact made 18 years ago, the immortals will send someone

58
00:03:53,260 --> 00:03:58,120
to the Mortal Realm at this time of the year to pray for us.

59
00:03:58,120 --> 00:04:00,900
I only remember that we used to sneak into the Imperial Kitchen

60
00:04:00,900 --> 00:04:03,850
and steal the offerings that were meant for the deities.

61
00:04:08,220 --> 00:04:09,620
I remember that too.

62
00:04:09,620 --> 00:04:11,573
I...

63
00:04:11,573 --> 00:04:15,860
At this time of the year, immortals will pray for the human race.

64
00:04:15,860 --> 00:04:18,200
The immortal emissary will bring them here.

65
00:04:18,200 --> 00:04:21,920
However, it only happens on the tenth day of the ninth month.

66
00:04:21,920 --> 00:04:24,870
Today's only the tenth day of the eighth month.

67
00:04:24,870 --> 00:04:32,200
What if we make them realize that the human race is in trouble and that they have to come down to pray for us?

68
00:04:38,580 --> 00:04:40,860
What's the situation? Lan'er is fine now.

69
00:04:40,860 --> 00:04:43,420
- He's already asleep.
- Good.

70
00:04:46,020 --> 00:04:47,580
This is the real deal.

71
00:04:47,580 --> 00:04:48,861
Look, this is real.
<i>[Jade]</i>

72
00:04:48,861 --> 00:04:51,760
It's the mark of the Jade Deity.

73
00:04:51,760 --> 00:04:55,920
No one in the four realms can copy this.

74
00:04:58,620 --> 00:05:03,680
- The girl looks so young, and she's not powerful.
- That's right.

75
00:05:03,680 --> 00:05:08,440
However, she owns the magic item created by the Jade Deity himself.

76
00:05:08,440 --> 00:05:12,560
It's obvious that she has a noble identity among the immortals.

77
00:05:12,560 --> 00:05:15,680
There's only one fairy that can fit the bill.

78
00:05:16,980 --> 00:05:21,080
<i>- She's the Heavenly Princess.
- She's the Heavenly Princess.</i>

79
00:05:21,080 --> 00:05:23,840
No wonder I thought she looked familiar.

80
00:05:23,840 --> 00:05:27,180
I saw her in Guixu before.

81
00:05:27,180 --> 00:05:30,440
Beast King, Beast Queen, can you listen to my explanation now?

82
00:05:30,440 --> 00:05:31,940
Don't explain yourself!

83
00:05:31,940 --> 00:05:35,300
- I...
- Before this, I thought she was a demoness.

84
00:05:35,300 --> 00:05:39,170
It'll be embarrassing if we let her reveal her true identity now.

85
00:05:39,170 --> 00:05:45,060
Why don't we pretend to be ignorant and set her up with Lan'er?

86
00:05:48,400 --> 00:05:50,900
I believe that no one in the Beast Realm

87
00:05:50,900 --> 00:05:56,880
can force Lan'er to extract his internal elixir, unless he did so willingly.

88
00:05:56,880 --> 00:06:00,600
He sacrificed himself because of you.

89
00:06:00,600 --> 00:06:06,620
We can see that you're very important to him.

90
00:06:06,620 --> 00:06:13,206
Of course, we were too rude to send you both to prison.

91
00:06:13,206 --> 00:06:17,206
Please forgive us, Miss.

92
00:06:17,206 --> 00:06:21,640
<i>They're pretty quick at changing their stances.</i>

93
00:06:21,640 --> 00:06:23,480
- Beast King.
- Miss, you'll forgive us?

94
00:06:23,480 --> 00:06:26,080
Thank you so much.

95
00:06:26,080 --> 00:06:31,040
Although Lan'er has absorbed the internal elixir, he needs to rest and recuperate.

96
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:35,600
- But—
- Of course, miss, I'm sure you were shocked since you were just released from prison.

97
00:06:35,600 --> 00:06:37,200
- I...
- What about this?

98
00:06:37,200 --> 00:06:41,800
You can spend your days keeping Lan'er company at the Prince's Mansion.

99
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:44,080
You can rest and recuperate there.

100
00:06:44,080 --> 00:06:45,290
- But...
- Servants!

101
00:06:45,290 --> 00:06:48,020
You two, bring the lady to the side chamber.

102
00:06:48,020 --> 00:06:49,440
- Yes, Your Majesty.
- Yes, Your Majesty. Do rest well.

103
00:06:49,440 --> 00:06:51,353
Please.

104
00:06:51,353 --> 00:06:53,173
Please.

105
00:06:53,173 --> 00:06:55,820
Do rest well.

106
00:06:55,820 --> 00:07:00,700
The immortal princess has a noble identity.

107
00:07:00,700 --> 00:07:06,740
If she does marry Lan'er, it'll be a joyous occasion for our tribe.

108
00:07:06,740 --> 00:07:08,480
You're right.

109
00:07:10,060 --> 00:07:12,820
However, the immortals of the Heavenly Realm are very prideful.

110
00:07:12,820 --> 00:07:18,860
If he finds out that his precious daughter came to the Beast Realm without his permission,

111
00:07:18,860 --> 00:07:20,680
he'll surely throw a thunderous fit.

112
00:07:20,680 --> 00:07:23,380
That's why we should keep this a secret for now.

113
00:07:23,380 --> 00:07:26,113
That's right.

114
00:07:26,113 --> 00:07:29,680
Our son only has eyes for that jinx from the Liguang family.

115
00:07:29,680 --> 00:07:33,491
Luckily, she has married off to the Void long ago.

116
00:07:33,491 --> 00:07:37,700
Now that the immortal princess is here,

117
00:07:37,700 --> 00:07:43,040
I don't need to worry about his relationship with that jinx.

118
00:07:43,040 --> 00:07:45,860
You're right.

119
00:07:54,900 --> 00:07:59,520
Sir, we only observe the stars once every six months.

120
00:07:59,520 --> 00:08:01,960
Why have we increased its frequency?

121
00:08:01,960 --> 00:08:07,410
Ever since the two princesses left, His Majesty has been feeling unwell and kept having headaches.

122
00:08:07,410 --> 00:08:09,520
Before this, anomalies were happening in Guixu.

123
00:08:09,520 --> 00:08:11,500
After that, a theft broke out in the palace.

124
00:08:11,500 --> 00:08:14,100
Lately, the human race has been experiencing misfortunes.

125
00:08:14,100 --> 00:08:16,620
I increased its frequency as I was afraid that something else might happen.

126
00:08:16,620 --> 00:08:20,000
At least we can take precautions if we discover any anomalies.

127
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:23,900
It's been over 30 years since the late Emperor gave me his final instruction.

128
00:08:23,900 --> 00:08:27,760
Sir, you've always been assisting His Majesty ever since he ascended the throne.

129
00:08:27,760 --> 00:08:29,360
You've done much for the people.

130
00:08:29,360 --> 00:08:33,560
Sir, you've done everything you could for the human race.

131
00:08:33,560 --> 00:08:37,400
I hope His Majesty can understand my intention.

132
00:08:37,400 --> 00:08:42,760
Back then, I suggest His Majesty execute Yetan, the Second Princess, to ensure the human race's safety.

133
00:08:42,760 --> 00:08:46,540
His Majesty might look like he respected my suggestion, but I think

134
00:08:46,540 --> 00:08:51,060
that was the beginning of our estrangement.

135
00:08:51,060 --> 00:08:55,580
Sir, your dedication to the human race is clear for all to see.

136
00:08:55,580 --> 00:08:57,980
His Majesty will understand it eventually.

137
00:08:57,980 --> 00:09:01,080
No matter how His Majesty thinks about me,

138
00:09:01,080 --> 00:09:05,646
I'll have peace of mind as long as the human race is safe.

139
00:09:05,646 --> 00:09:09,000
By the way, pass the star chart to me.

140
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:12,440
As long as the human race is safe, huh?

141
00:09:12,440 --> 00:09:17,180
Today, I'll make sure this old fool and Liguang Yang have a hard time together.

142
00:09:30,340 --> 00:09:34,090
This is the jinx star, Rooftop Swallow Mansion!

143
00:09:34,090 --> 00:09:36,400
How did it appear all of a sudden?

144
00:09:36,400 --> 00:09:38,401
It's an enormous omen! Yes!

145
00:09:38,401 --> 00:09:41,501
- Report this to His Majesty immediately. Hurry!
- Yes.

146
00:09:47,640 --> 00:09:50,920
Your Majesty, your headaches are getting worse.

147
00:09:50,920 --> 00:09:54,920
In the future, you should stop tiring yourself out over state matters.

148
00:09:54,920 --> 00:09:59,360
After the occurrence of the Guixu anomaly, the human race, which has no power, suffered the most losses.

149
00:09:59,360 --> 00:10:00,740
I'm the ruler of the realm.

150
00:10:00,740 --> 00:10:02,260
How could I slack off?

151
00:10:02,260 --> 00:10:04,610
This headache is nothing.

152
00:10:04,610 --> 00:10:09,080
Your Majesty, you mentioned that you couldn't sleep well lately because you dreamed of the princesses.

153
00:10:09,080 --> 00:10:12,993
Are you worried that they might not be doing well?

154
00:10:12,993 --> 00:10:17,180
Lately, in my dreams, they had no place to go and no food to eat.

155
00:10:17,180 --> 00:10:19,180
Your Majesty, dreams always show the opposite scenarios.

156
00:10:19,180 --> 00:10:21,980
That means they're doing well now.

157
00:10:22,680 --> 00:10:25,520
Yes. I guess I'm overthinking it.

158
00:10:25,520 --> 00:10:28,660
Right now, they're protected by the two strongest races in the four realms.

159
00:10:28,660 --> 00:10:31,400
It's much safer than staying with us.

160
00:10:31,400 --> 00:10:34,111
I no longer need to worry about them.

161
00:10:34,111 --> 00:10:35,860
Your Majesty, wait!

162
00:10:35,860 --> 00:10:39,560
- Stop! Lower the carriage!
- Your Majesty, wait!

163
00:10:39,560 --> 00:10:42,360
Your Majesty, I have pressing matters to report to you.

164
00:10:42,360 --> 00:10:44,040
My loyal subject, what's the urgency?

165
00:10:44,040 --> 00:10:48,880
When I was observing the stars, the jinx star, Rooftop Swallow Mansion, appeared out of nowhere.

166
00:10:48,880 --> 00:10:51,280
It's an extremely ill omen.

167
00:10:51,280 --> 00:10:55,300
Since the jinx star flew into the sky, it will descend eventually.

168
00:10:55,300 --> 00:10:57,220
I was afraid that the public might be terrified.

169
00:10:57,220 --> 00:10:59,980
That's why I came to report the issue.

170
00:10:59,980 --> 00:11:03,540
No wonder misfortunes have been happening often lately.

171
00:11:03,540 --> 00:11:05,920
Every year, the immortals will perform a ceremony for the human race

172
00:11:05,920 --> 00:11:08,580
to dispel all misfortunes and enhance good fortunes.

173
00:11:08,580 --> 00:11:13,280
For this year's ceremony, we must request the immortals to dispel our misfortunes for us.

174
00:11:13,280 --> 00:11:15,920
There's one month left before the prayer ceremony.

175
00:11:15,920 --> 00:11:19,520
However, the ill omen of the Rooftop Swallow Mansion will come true by tomorrow!

176
00:11:19,520 --> 00:11:23,200
I'm afraid the one-month gap will bring disaster to the country!

177
00:11:23,200 --> 00:11:25,960
Your Majesty, please write to the immortals immediately

178
00:11:25,960 --> 00:11:30,420
and request them to come in advance to proceed with the prayer ceremony.

179
00:11:30,420 --> 00:11:31,820
You do have a point.

180
00:11:31,820 --> 00:11:34,040
I'll write to the immortals right now.

181
00:11:34,040 --> 00:11:37,080
Your Majesty, be careful. Here.

182
00:11:37,080 --> 00:11:39,240
Raise the carriage.

183
00:11:54,000 --> 00:11:55,433
Qingheng?

184
00:11:55,433 --> 00:11:57,110
- Sister-in-law.
- Qingheng!

185
00:11:57,110 --> 00:11:59,760
Sister-in-law, how was it? Did they fall for it?

186
00:11:59,760 --> 00:12:02,920
Of course. Just now, that old dog...

187
00:12:04,840 --> 00:12:08,301
I mean, the Grand Chancellor, was shocked when he saw the Rooftop Swallow Mansion.

188
00:12:08,301 --> 00:12:13,061
He rushed to my father and told him to hold the prayer ceremony in advance.

189
00:12:13,061 --> 00:12:15,070
Sister-in-law, you're a prophet indeed.

190
00:12:15,070 --> 00:12:17,380
So, what should we do next?

191
00:12:17,380 --> 00:12:20,980
I've already come up with a solution.

192
00:12:24,980 --> 00:12:29,020
<i>During the prayer ceremony, my father will take a bath and get changed to show his sincerity.</i>

193
00:12:29,020 --> 00:12:36,020
<i>By then, I can delay him with my tricks for at least an hour.</i>

194
00:12:43,820 --> 00:12:45,440
Where's my ceremonial suit?

195
00:12:45,440 --> 00:12:47,690
Where's my ceremonial suit?

196
00:12:47,690 --> 00:12:52,500
Useless fools! You can't even do your job well?

197
00:12:52,500 --> 00:12:54,580
The deities have been waiting for a long time.

198
00:12:54,580 --> 00:12:57,200
All of you will be executed if the prayer ceremony is delayed!

199
00:12:57,200 --> 00:13:00,100
I'll kill you all! I'll kill you all!

200
00:13:00,100 --> 00:13:01,660
- Your Majesty, have mercy!
- Your Majesty, have mercy!

201
00:13:01,660 --> 00:13:02,740
- <i>Your Majesty, have mercy!</i>
- <i>Your Majesty, have mercy!</i>

202
00:13:02,740 --> 00:13:06,700
- Man Man, by then, you can impersonate my father.
- Me?

203
00:13:06,700 --> 00:13:09,890
You will meet up with the immortal emissary first.

204
00:13:14,340 --> 00:13:16,280
Welcome, Empyrean.

205
00:13:16,280 --> 00:13:19,080
Welcome, Empyrean.

206
00:13:23,540 --> 00:13:25,180
There was a sense of foreboding when we read the stars.

207
00:13:25,180 --> 00:13:27,380
We had no choice but to hold the prayer ceremony in advance.

208
00:13:27,380 --> 00:13:29,400
Empyrean, please forgive us.

209
00:13:29,940 --> 00:13:31,573
It's nothing.

210
00:13:32,060 --> 00:13:32,940
Please.

211
00:13:32,940 --> 00:13:35,300
The prayer ceremony is held every year.

212
00:13:35,300 --> 00:13:37,520
The Ministry of Immortal Rites has gotten everything ready in advance.

213
00:13:37,520 --> 00:13:40,200
<i>I just had to depart a few days earlier.</i>

214
00:13:40,200 --> 00:13:43,000
<i>Emperor Tun, are you still suffering from headaches?</i>

215
00:13:43,000 --> 00:13:45,620
Empyrean, I was elated when I heard that you were coming.

216
00:13:45,620 --> 00:13:48,240
I feel much better now.

217
00:13:50,020 --> 00:13:51,553
Laugh!

218
00:13:52,260 --> 00:13:53,593
Laugh!

219
00:13:55,540 --> 00:13:58,820
Empyrean, we'll have to depend on you for the prayer ceremony.

220
00:13:58,820 --> 00:14:01,200
This is part of my duty.

221
00:14:01,200 --> 00:14:04,050
Emperor Tun, you need not be courteous.

222
00:14:04,050 --> 00:14:05,040
Empyrean, please.

223
00:14:05,040 --> 00:14:06,840
Emperor Tun, please.

224
00:14:13,220 --> 00:14:16,553
Empyrean, I've admired the immortals' tools of rites for a long time.

225
00:14:16,553 --> 00:14:18,640
May I have a look?

226
00:14:27,300 --> 00:14:29,760
It's divine indeed.

227
00:14:30,580 --> 00:14:34,540
Man Man will impersonate Father and meet up with the immortal emissary.

228
00:14:34,540 --> 00:14:39,460
After that, we'll swap the real deal with a fake one.

229
00:14:45,300 --> 00:14:47,160
You.

230
00:14:47,160 --> 00:14:52,220
Bring the Empyrean to inspect the prayer altar.

231
00:14:52,220 --> 00:14:54,100
- Empyrean, please.
- Empyrean, please.

232
00:14:54,100 --> 00:14:55,513
Sure.

233
00:15:15,400 --> 00:15:18,220
You're amazing!

234
00:15:28,960 --> 00:15:31,560
What do you think about my plan?

235
00:15:33,840 --> 00:15:35,260
