00:32:38,900 --> 00:32:40,060
The ceremony is done!

490
00:32:40,060 --> 00:32:41,693
Wait!

491
00:32:43,600 --> 00:32:48,860
Empyrean, although you've skipped most of the rites,

492
00:32:48,860 --> 00:32:52,520
I still have a question.

493
00:32:52,520 --> 00:32:54,520
Emperor Tun, ask away.

494
00:32:55,420 --> 00:32:57,420
I have two daughters.

495
00:32:57,420 --> 00:33:01,180
Although they've been sent to the immortals and voidwalkers
respectively,

496
00:33:01,180 --> 00:33:07,260
in my heart, they're still descendants of the Liguang family.

497
00:33:07,260 --> 00:33:13,280
I'm worried that the ill omen might implicate them.

498
00:33:13,280 --> 00:33:18,410
I wonder if they were included as recipients of the blessings too?

499
00:33:19,980 --> 00:33:21,840
Emperor Tun, don't worry.

500
00:33:21,840 --> 00:33:25,120
Since you're the one initiating the ceremony,

501
00:33:25,120 --> 00:33:28,600
the blessings will be shared with the entire human race,

502
00:33:28,600 --> 00:33:30,800
including the two princesses.

503
00:33:30,800 --> 00:33:33,200
If so, I can rest at ease now.

504
00:33:36,920 --> 00:33:39,760
<i>When the sun sets, </i>

505
00:33:39,760 --> 00:33:44,580
<i>Dear will bring the Purifying Vial here to extinguish the flame.</i>

506
00:33:45,400 --> 00:33:52,200
<i>By then, we can leave.</i>

507
00:34:01,760 --> 00:34:04,380
Sir, it's my first time seeing you acting like this.

508
00:34:04,380 --> 00:34:07,280
You wasted so much time because of Princess Qingkui.

509
00:34:07,280 --> 00:34:10,960
Just when we finally got her drunk, you just had to carry her back to the inn.

510
00:34:10,960 --> 00:34:14,520
You prepared some hangover soup for her as you were afraid that she might have a hangover.

511
00:34:14,520 --> 00:34:17,920
And you even prepared a meal for her just in case she might be hungry.

512
00:34:17,920 --> 00:34:19,880
"Oh, my dear Kui'er."

513
00:34:19,880 --> 00:34:22,280
Sir!

514
00:34:22,280 --> 00:34:25,660
It'll be too late for us to regret it if we waste our opportunity because of this.

515
00:34:25,660 --> 00:34:27,640
Are you done nagging?

516
00:34:27,640 --> 00:34:29,173
Shut up.

517
00:34:54,600 --> 00:34:57,720
Sir, is that redhead guy Shaodian Youqin?

518
00:34:57,720 --> 00:35:01,700
This redhead demon doesn't have the flair of an empyrean.

519
00:35:01,700 --> 00:35:07,040
If I'm not mistaken, Shaodian Youqin lost all his power after mending Guixu.

520
00:35:07,040 --> 00:35:10,210
And he was caught in a fight too. He's already a shadow of his former self.

521
00:35:12,740 --> 00:35:14,420
He's not Shaodian Youqin.

522
00:35:14,420 --> 00:35:16,960
He's just a soul shard.

523
00:35:18,980 --> 00:35:24,220
Seems like Yetan came here to gather the soul shards to revive Shaodian Youqin.

524
00:35:25,900 --> 00:35:29,600
No wonder Princess Qingkui was trying her best to hide this from us.

525
00:35:29,600 --> 00:35:31,540
This soul shard is dumb and weak.

526
00:35:31,540 --> 00:35:34,100
He's no match for you.

527
00:35:45,640 --> 00:35:47,373
Go away!

528
00:35:52,420 --> 00:35:55,020
I said, go away!

529
00:36:00,060 --> 00:36:01,810
He's pretty grumpy.

530
00:36:05,920 --> 00:36:08,070
Let's end this quickly.

531
00:36:20,660 --> 00:36:24,540
Initially, I thought I would ascend the throne after killing Eldest and Second Brother.

532
00:36:24,540 --> 00:36:29,760
I never expected Heaven to assign the hero of the four realms to be my last opponent.

533
00:36:36,280 --> 00:36:39,440
It's your fate to die here.

534
00:36:39,440 --> 00:36:41,800
Die.

535
00:36:52,540 --> 00:36:56,220
Shaodian Youqin, don't blame me for kicking you when you're down.

536
00:36:56,220 --> 00:36:57,540
You care for the world.

537
00:36:57,540 --> 00:36:59,200
And all living beings are indebted to you.

538
00:36:59,200 --> 00:37:01,600
However, I have someone who I need to protect even at the expense of my life!

539
00:37:01,600 --> 00:37:06,340
For Consort Mother and Kui'er's sake, you have to die!

540
00:37:07,800 --> 00:37:09,060
Chaofeng!

541
00:37:09,060 --> 00:37:10,693
Your Highness!

542
00:37:37,760 --> 00:37:39,380
- Su Shui!
- Chaofeng, you mustn't go!

543
00:37:39,380 --> 00:37:41,460
I haven't settled the scores with you for taking the Princess to the Mortal Realm without permission.

544
00:37:41,460 --> 00:37:43,140
- Let go!
- Why did you bring her here?
- No!

545
00:37:43,140 --> 00:37:45,760
- Kui'er!
- She pressured me with Consort Xue right after you guys left.

546
00:37:45,760 --> 00:37:49,100
She said... She said she wouldn't treat my family if I didn't let her come here.

547
00:37:49,100 --> 00:37:50,820
- What can I do?
- You!

548
00:37:50,820 --> 00:37:52,753
Let go!

549
00:37:53,420 --> 00:37:55,200
If you wish to kill the soul shard, you have to kill me first!

550
00:37:55,200 --> 00:37:57,620
- Don't go there!
- This is none of your business.

551
00:37:57,620 --> 00:37:59,040
Royal Father has already issued an order.

552
00:37:59,040 --> 00:38:01,660
The one who kills Shaodian Youqin will be the next crown prince.

553
00:38:01,660 --> 00:38:03,680
This is my best opportunity.

554
00:38:03,680 --> 00:38:06,580
Didn't you say that you were protecting me because you couldn't bear

555
00:38:06,580 --> 00:38:10,520
to see me and Tan'er get implicated because of the power struggle?

556
00:38:10,520 --> 00:38:13,160
You said you didn't care for power, but you cared about loyalty.

557
00:38:13,160 --> 00:38:15,460
You said you were different from Wu Dai, Dingyun, and the rest.

558
00:38:15,460 --> 00:38:17,020
But look at what you're doing right now.

559
00:38:17,020 --> 00:38:19,760
Before this, I tried to delay your progress and protect the soul shard

560
00:38:19,760 --> 00:38:22,099
because I didn't want you to be tempted by the crown prince's throne

561
00:38:22,099 --> 00:38:25,320
and become a sinner of the four realms for killing the soul shard!

562
00:38:25,320 --> 00:38:29,160
The battle for the crown prince's throne concerns our survival.

563
00:38:29,160 --> 00:38:31,900
Right now, there's an opportunity in front of me.

564
00:38:31,900 --> 00:38:33,640
I can't just give it up.

565
00:38:33,640 --> 00:38:35,400
Stay out of this.

566
00:38:35,400 --> 00:38:38,880
- Get out of the way!
- Chaofeng! No!

567
00:38:38,880 --> 00:38:41,980
I'll say yes to anything else.

568
00:38:41,980 --> 00:38:44,480
But I can't just let you do the wrong thing.

569
00:38:44,480 --> 00:38:47,420
If you kill the hero, the immortals will fall out with the voidwalkers

570
00:38:47,420 --> 00:38:49,920
and plunge the four realms into chaos again!

571
00:38:52,720 --> 00:38:54,320
You care about Yetan.

572
00:38:54,320 --> 00:38:55,960
You care about the soul shard.

573
00:38:55,960 --> 00:38:58,180
You care about the immortals and the humans, morality and justice.

574
00:38:58,180 --> 00:38:59,960
What about me? Have you considered my feelings?

575
00:38:59,960 --> 00:39:03,900
I'm persuading you to stop precisely because I care about you.

576
00:39:03,900 --> 00:39:06,700
Once you kill the soul shard, you'll become the Crown Prince.

577
00:39:06,700 --> 00:39:10,200
You'll become the next bloodthirsty Void Tyrant!

578
00:39:10,200 --> 00:39:13,150
When that happens, there will be no turning back!

579
00:39:15,480 --> 00:39:17,213
Chaofeng!

580
00:39:18,080 --> 00:39:22,620
If you care about me too, stop now, please.

581
00:39:30,560 --> 00:39:34,920
<i>Fiery, I promised you that I would bring back the Purifying Vial before the sun sets.</i>

582
00:39:34,920 --> 00:39:37,080
<i>I'll keep my promise. Wait for me just a little longer.</i>

583
00:39:37,080 --> 00:39:38,660
<i>You'll be free soon.</i>

584
00:39:38,660 --> 00:39:42,100
<i>This is bad. I used too much power when I impersonated Emperor Tun.</i>

585
00:39:42,100 --> 00:39:45,160
<i>I don't think I can maintain this form. You both should be careful.</i>

586
00:39:57,720 --> 00:39:59,040
My back!

587
00:39:59,040 --> 00:40:00,520
Are you okay?

588
00:40:00,520 --> 00:40:03,270
I can't move anymore. You guys should go.

589
00:40:03,840 --> 00:40:05,400
Go now.

590
00:40:05,400 --> 00:40:07,860
Stay here, okay?

591
00:40:07,860 --> 00:40:09,493
Let's go!

592
00:40:43,760 --> 00:40:45,793
Chaofeng!

593
00:40:59,020 --> 00:41:01,260
Soul shard!

594
00:41:01,260 --> 00:41:02,280
Kui'er!

595
00:41:02,280 --> 00:41:03,740
- Your Highness!
- Soul shard!

596
00:41:03,740 --> 00:41:05,580
This is the immortals' Southern Brightness Sacred Fire.

597
00:41:05,580 --> 00:41:07,980
When it ignites, it'll burn the land even if it's thousands of li away.

598
00:41:07,980 --> 00:41:10,100
- Let's go!
- No!

599
00:41:10,100 --> 00:41:11,840
- Let's go! Let's go!
- Go and save the soul shard!

600
00:41:11,840 --> 00:41:14,200
Let's go! Let's go!

601
00:41:40,080 --> 00:41:43,200
If you want to burn someone, burn me!

602
00:42:07,880 --> 00:42:09,060
Fire!

603
00:42:09,060 --> 00:42:10,280
Fire! Hurry!

604
00:42:10,280 --> 00:42:12,500
Run! Fire!

605
00:42:12,500 --> 00:42:14,600
Run away! Hurry!

606
00:42:14,600 --> 00:42:15,960
Hurry!

607
00:42:15,960 --> 00:42:17,893
Fire!

608
00:43:12,740 --> 00:43:17,840
<i>"Flawless World" - Mao Buyi</i>

609
00:43:17,840 --> 00:43:23,220
♫ <i>You say, "Light swept through the twin flowers"</i> ♫

610
00:43:23,220 --> 00:43:29,980
♫ <i>Wandering at the desolate cliff</i> ♫

611
00:43:29,980 --> 00:43:35,380
♫ <i>Whose face has the wind comfort again?</i> ♫

612
00:43:35,380 --> 00:43:42,100
♫ <i>When the seabed sands are flying everywhere</i> ♫

613
00:43:42,100 --> 00:43:48,260
♫ <i>If only I can spend the sorrowful night with you</i> ♫

614
00:43:48,260 --> 00:43:54,200
♫ <i>We'll go through the ups and downs together</i> ♫

615
00:43:54,200 --> 00:44:00,080
♫ <i>Hair being messed up by the misplaced time and space</i> ♫

616
00:44:00,080 --> 00:44:06,360
♫ <i>No matter how tough it is, i'm not afraid</i> ♫

617
00:44:06,360 --> 00:44:11,846
♫ <i>You are the crescent in my heart</i> ♫

618
00:44:11,846 --> 00:44:18,640
♫ <i>My radiant light shining through the years</i> ♫

619
00:44:18,640 --> 00:44:30,900
♫ <i>If I do shed tears, they will turn into flowers in my heart</i> ♫

620
00:44:30,900 --> 00:44:36,166
♫ <i>I'll always be the unchanging love in your heart</i> ♫

621
00:44:36,166 --> 00:44:42,933
♫ <i>Even the galaxy will agree with me, love needs no answer</i> ♫

622
00:44:42,933 --> 00:44:48,180
♫ <i>I'll shine for you</i> ♫

623
00:44:48,180 --> 00:44:55,120
♫ <i>In this flawless world</i> ♫

624
00:44:55,120 --> 00:45:01,080
♫ <i>I'll always be the unchanging love in your heart</i> ♫

625
00:45:01,080 --> 00:45:08,840
♫ <i>In this flawless world</i> ♫
